=head1 NAME

ExtUtils::testlib - add blib/* directories to @INC

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  use ExtUtils::testlib;

=head1 DESCRIPTION

After an extension has been built and before it is installed it may be
desirable to test it bypassing C<make test>. By adding

    use ExtUtils::testlib;

